Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.37,0:00:05.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎來到羅德斯島
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.50,0:00:08.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼緊接著\N就請觀賞第二部份吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.37,0:00:11.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,~歡迎來到羅德斯島~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.48,0:00:14.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮絲，妳的感冒好像好了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.35,0:00:16.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，沒有生病的感覺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.69,0:00:19.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目的地大龍山就在眼前囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.19,0:00:20.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.19,0:00:22.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.39,0:00:23.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.70,0:00:24.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就快到了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.07,0:00:27.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗妖精跑哪去啦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.30,0:00:31.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我命令他一定要搶到餅乾的\N現在卻還沒搶到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.70,0:00:32.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼回事啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.27,0:00:36.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是這樣的話\N就讓我去試試把餅乾搶來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.11,0:00:37.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.28,0:00:39.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請拭目以待好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.15,0:00:42.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,視而不見的微小精靈啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.35,0:00:45.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將我的身影與你同化吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.85,0:00:47.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(咒文)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.35,0:00:49.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔!好精彩!都看不到!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.39,0:00:50.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太厲害了，比蘿天絲!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.98,0:00:52.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也教我這招吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.23,0:00:54.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是，阿修拉姆大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.60,0:00:59.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?哎呀?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.50,0:01:03.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮絲妳在幹嘛?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.87,0:01:05.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,籃子被拉住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.54,0:01:07.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦?哼哼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.24,0:01:10.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然…\N看招!看招!看招…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.04,0:01:12.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀!好癢!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:12.04,0:01:13.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.15,0:01:15.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你對比蘿天絲做了什麼\N饒不了你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:15.61,0:01:17.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出現了!有鬼啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.59,0:01:24.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊!好燙好燙…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.86,0:01:27.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿修拉姆大人，快把披風脫掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:27.49,0:01:29.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，撤退!\N是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.46,0:01:31.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什、什麼啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.60,0:01:36.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇!阿修拉姆大人，你的屁股…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.74,0:01:37.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?屁股?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.47,0:01:42.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊!啊!我的內褲?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.07,0:01:43.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀!討厭!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.68,0:01:45.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那是什麼啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.91,0:01:47.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這，我也不曉得…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.38,0:01:52.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 來，我們快走吧\N- 好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.89,0:01:54.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我一生最大的恥辱!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.59,0:01:56.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然光著身子被部下看到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.36,0:01:59.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記得再看喔
